Step 5: Run the following commands to install s/w
1.	Update all softwares in Ubuntu by command
sudo apt update
2.	Install docker by command
sudo apt-get install docker.io
3.	Install git by command
sudo apt install git
4.	Install nano( text editor) by command
Sudo apt install nano





: Open git Bash in folder Example by right clicking with mouse
In git bash run the following commands
git init
git add .
git commit -m "first commit"

In AWS in git
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/pranavreddy2006/AWS.git
git push -u origin main



